
Base UX

Deposits: minutes

Withdrawals: ~7 days to L1 (typical for Optimistic L2s)

Extremely reliable RPCs and infra thanks to Coinbase

zkSync UX

Deposits: seconds

Withdrawals: minutes

Near-instant inclusion into ZK batches

UX feels “L1-like” for high-velocity apps

Verdict:
zkSync is unmatched for withdrawals and instant finality.
